[src:mocha-chai/api-bdd-p01] When the target is a string or array, `.empty` asserts that the target’s `length` property is strictly (`===`) equal to `0`.
[src:mocha-chai/api-bdd-p01] When the target is a map or set, `.empty` asserts that the target’s `size` property is strictly equal to `0`.
